data.value:
This program can be used to update the contact information for ECSA Executives on the ECSA website: www.ualberta.ca/~ecvhouse
It first tries to load the current executives.json file from the server which specifies all the contact information that is displayed on the website. If it can't load this file, then there is most likely some sort of issue, see if you can access the file yourself on the filesystem.
Once it is able to load the file, you can begin changing the various information, but make sure to click 'Save' once you're done updating. This program will try to load the current picture for each Executive. You can change which picture will be displayed on the website by clicking 'Update Picture', and selecting the new picture.
If the Executive Positions have changed, you can click the 'Positions...' button to update them. The drop down list will then update according to the positions specified, and you can specify new information/picture for any new positions.
If you have any questions about this program, feel free to email dylan.stank@gmail.com
